# GrooveStation 🎵

A simple web-based Drum Machine built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
This project is inspired by the freeCodeCamp Drum Machine lab but styled and customized with my own design.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Nine interactive drum pads mapped to keys **Q, W, E, A, S, D, Z, X, C**.
- Click or press the keyboard keys to trigger sounds.
- Displays the name of the sound currently being played.
- Accessible design with clear labels and responsive layout.
- Lightweight and easy to run in any modern browser.

---

## 🖥️ User Stories Implemented
- `#drum-machine` container holds all elements.
- `#pad-bank` contains nine clickable drum pads.
- Each pad has an embedded `<audio>` element with a unique sound.
- Pads respond to both **mouse clicks** and **keyboard presses**.
- The `#display` element shows the name of the triggered sound.

---

